of our play. Taking the rook loses.} 19. Qxe5 {White is trying to trade queens
and save himself.} Qa3 {Keeps the tension!} 20. Qxb2 Qxg3 {White has to be
accurate here to maintain the balance. Bf6 is incoming.} *

