sacrifice.} exd5 13. Nf5 Kf8 14. Qg3 {Loses, but Black really should know how
to defend himself here.} dxe4 15. Bxe4 Bxe4 16. Rxe4 Qc5 {I think this is a
very hard move to find. Good to know it.} 17. Bh6 {Looks scary, but here Black
can just go down the forced line} Nxe4 18. Qxg7+ Ke8 19. Qxh8+ Nf8 {And White
is just a piece down.} *

